definition.text: Upsampling layer for 2D inputs. Repeats the rows and columns of the data by size[0] and size[1] respectively.

translations.text: Слой апсемплинга для двумерных входных данных. Повторяет строки и столбцы данных на size[0] и size[1] соответственно.

paragraphs.text: Input shape: 4D tensor with shape: - If dataFormat is "channelsLast": [batch, rows, cols, channels] - If dataFormat is "channelsFirst": [batch, channels, rows, cols]

translations.text: Input shape: 4D тензор с формой: - Если dataFormat - "channelsLast": [batch, rows, cols, channels] - Если dataFormat - "channelsFirst": [batch, channels, rows, cols].

paragraphs.text: Output shape: 4D tensor with shape: - If dataFormat is "channelsLast": [batch, upsampledRows, upsampledCols, channels] - If dataFormat is "channelsFirst": [batch, channels, upsampledRows, upsampledCols]

translations.text: Output shape: 4D тензор с формой: - Если dataFormat - "channelsLast": [batch, upsampledRows, upsampledCols, channels] - Если dataFormat - "channelsFirst": [batch, channels, upsampledRows, upsampledCols].
